Class JBCollection

java.lang.Object
it.unipv.ingsfw.JavaBeats.model.collection.JBCollection
All Implemented Interfaces:
IJBResearchable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Album, Playlist, Podcast
public abstract class JBCollection extends Object implements IJBResearchable
Abstract class representing a generic JavaBeats collection. Contains attributes and methods common to Album, Playlist and Podcast.
